    <h1>Concurrency Control</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Wikipedia &middot; <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Concurrency_control"><img src="/reading/wikipedia.svg" alt="wp" style="display:inline;height:1em;vertical-align:-0.1em;margin-right:0.2em;"/>Concurrency control</a> &middot; CC BY-SA 4.0</p>

    <div class="bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8 callout">
      <p class="text-lg" style="max-width:none"><strong>Concurrency control</strong> ensures that concurrent transactions produce correct results. The main techniques: locking (pessimistic: block conflicts before they happen), optimistic concurrency control (validate at commit time), and MVCC (each transaction sees a consistent snapshot).</p>
    </div>

    <!-- SVG: Lock compatibility matrix -->
    <div class="flex justify-center my-6">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 300 160" class="w-full max-w-xs" style="font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;">
        <!-- Title -->
        <text x="150" y="20" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor" font-size="11" fill-opacity="0.7">Lock Compatibility Matrix</text>

        <!-- Headers -->
        <text x="150" y="50" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor" font-size="10" fill-opacity="0.5">Requested</text>
        <text x="40" y="80" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor" font-size="10" fill-opacity="0.5" transform="rotate(-90 40 80)">Held</text>

        <text x="170" y="68" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor" font-size="10" fill-opacity="0.7">S</text>
        <text x="230" y="68" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor" font-size="10" fill-opacity="0.7">X</text>

        <!-- Row: S held -->
        <text x="100" y="95" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor" font-size="10" fill-opacity="0.7">S</text>
        <rect x="148" y="82" width="40" height="20" rx="3" fill="#34d399" fill-opacity="0.15"/>
        <text x="170" y="96" text-anchor="middle" fill="#34d399" font-size="11">Yes</text>
        <rect x="210" y="82" width="40" height="20" rx="3" fill="#f87171" fill-opacity="0.15"/>
        <text x="230" y="96" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f87171" font-size="11">No</text>

        <!-- Row: X held -->
